-- Egypt Army to Soon Issue Statement on Constitution, Ahram Says
-- B y   T a r e k   E l - T a b l a w y
-- 2012-06-17T09:04:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-17/egypt-army-to-soon-issue-statement-on-constitution-ahram-says.html
Egypt ’s ruling military council will
issue a declaration within hours that stresses the need for the
drafting of a new constitution within three months, the state-
run Al-Ahram reported.  New parliamentary elections would be held and a committee
charged with drafting the charter will also be formed, the
newspaper reported, citing Sameh Ashour, head of the military
council’s civilian advisory body.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Tarek El-Tablawy in Cairo at 
